sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant S as SendMessageProcessor〔R5.5〕
    participant D as DefaultMessageStore〔R5.5〕
    participant L as CommitLog〔R5.5〕
    participant M as DefaultMappedFile〔R5.5〕
    participant F as FlushManager〔R5.5〕
    participant R as ReputMessageService〔R5.5〕
    participant Q as ConsumeQueue/IndexFile

    C->>S: 发送消息
    S->>D: asyncPutMessage
    D->>L: asyncPutMessage
    L->>L: 分配 QueueOffset、编码、加写锁
    L->>M: appendMessage
    M-->>L: wroteOffset + wroteBytes
    L->>F: handleDiskFlush
    F-->>C: 根据刷盘/复制条件完成结果
    R->>L: 从 reputFromOffset 顺序解析
    R->>Q: doDispatch 构建 CQ 与 Index
    R-->>R: 推进 reputFromOffset
